# Optional: enable real form submissions on the Contact section via Formspree.
#
# 1. Create a free form at https://formspree.io
# 2. Copy the endpoint it gives you (looks like https://formspree.io/f/xxxxxxx)
# 3. Paste it below and rename this file to ".env"
#
# If this is left empty, the Contact form falls back to opening the
# visitor's email client with a pre-filled message (mailto:) instead —
# no fake "message sent" confirmation is ever shown without a real backend.
VITE_FORMSPREE_ENDPOINT=

# Optional: also send a WhatsApp notification for every Contact form
# submission, via CallMeBot (https://www.callmebot.com) — a free "notify me"
# webhook, not a general WhatsApp API. Note: since this is a static site with
# no backend, these values are visible in the browser's network/JS — that's
# expected for CallMeBot's use case (only your own phone can receive these
# notifications), but don't reuse this API key anywhere sensitive.
#
# 1. Add +34 644 59 71 30 as a WhatsApp contact
# 2. Message it exactly: "I allow callmebot to send me messages"
# 3. It replies with your APIKey
# 4. Fill in both values below (phone in international format, no "+")
VITE_CALLMEBOT_PHONE=
VITE_CALLMEBOT_APIKEY=
